text: Shuwa may mean *Shuwa Arabic, the Afro-Arabic language spoken in Sudan, Chad and other states of Sahelian Africa *The mostly Arab speakers of this language also known as Baggara *The Japanese Sign Language (手話) *Honinbo Shuwa, a Japanese professional go player *Shuwaa, a roasted goat or lamb dish popular in Oman and the UAE
title: Shuwa
